Ace Singer Tuface Idibia has a message for those trolling his wife online. His wife Annie Idibia was said to have unfollowed him on his Instagram account, a speculation to which Annie denied blaming the outcome on a “glitch’ on the part of Instagram. Hours after that, another speculation rose that she was yet at loggerheads with her husband’s baby mama Pero. Netizens of course did not take it easy on the actress as they called her names and said she was the one at fault.   Actress Onyii Alexx calls out NDLEA over home invasion     Fresh suit seeks Atiku’s disqualification over…     Buhari seeks govs’ support in selection of APC presidential…   Rising to her defence, Tu Face told them to back off. He wrote: “Una can like to read nonsense meaning to everything Can’t somebody feel free again” Expressing himself in pidgin the singer added: “You all are wont to bullying people on social media and I do not understand. “You all should just leave my wife alone please, leave her alone.”